snippet.title: The Sims 4 Dine Out: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Own a restaurant and take your Sims out to eat with The Sims 4 Dine Out.
 
Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/4339 
 
Create and manage a variety of restaurants, hire staff, and set the perfect menu to earn a profit and expand your business. Dine out with Sims to enjoy all-new experimental cuisine and spend quality time with friends and family.
